node.text: Our newest space at 515 Madison opened earlier this year and we're celebrating by giving away a day pass and a pair of AirPods to use while you work! To enter, 1) follow @jaysuites, 2) tag 3) Tag 3 friends or coworkers. Add this post to your stories for 5 extra entries. Contest begins at 2:30pm CST on 3/12 and ends at 11:59pm CST on 3/20/2020. Must be 21 or over to enter and live in the New York metro area. Free office visit is available Monday - Friday 9am to 5pm. Winners will be announced on 3/23/2020.
